# Shop-Bill-Paper-Generator
A shop keeper can easily make a bill by just adding the products and their price in .csv file and then a bill be generated once he run this software.

Steps to make a bill paper:-

1. create a bill.csv file in your pc (create in same directory where you have billPaperGenerator.exe file).
2. Open bill.csv any time a customer buy some products.
      Now, type your shop name in the first line.
      In second line type your shop address.
      In third line just enter the tax (Like gst) percentage.
      Now, from fourth line, enter the product name and the price.
3. Execute billPaperGenerator.exe in your pc.
      On executing .exe file customer shopping bill paper will be opened in a notepad. so now you can print it directly from notepad.

